{
  "texts": [
    "Section IV-C).Lastly, we should not ignore the contribution of structureaware mutation.",
    "To trigger this bug, a minimal message sequence is required: SETUP → PLAY → PAUSE → PLAY.",
    "Omitting any of these messages will render the bug untriggerable.",
    "Existing mutation-based fuzzers, with their structureunaware mutation approach, have a high likelihood of breaking the message structures and rendering them invalid.",
    "In contrast, by utilizing the grammar derived from the LLM, structureaware mutation efficiently maintains the validity of messages.CHATAFL discovered 9 distinct, previously unknown bugs while AFLNET and NSFUZZ only discovered 3 and 4 of those, respectively."
  ]
}